title: Cabelas.Survival.Shadows.of.Katmai.PS3-DUPLEX
description: Play as Logan James, a bush pilot flying his plane that crashes in a desolate region of far-off Alaska. Isolated and at the mercy of an inhospitable nature, you have to fight against ferocious predators, face icy chasms and advance through caves where no one has ever set foot. And as if that were not enough, the harsh climate and deadly predators, you will also need to complete a mysterious mission. Can you survive?
